हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description:
On his father’s birthday, a son presents a gift no one dares to touch. But inside the box lies a truth strong enough to shatter egos, fortunes, and long-held silence.
A haunting tale of family, pride, and the price of secrets—where opening the past changes everything.
